social_posts.post_text: Headed to LA for Abella’s first concert and we came across these amazing blossomed trees 😍 kicking myself for not having my canon with me but my iPhone camera pulled through for me!

Abella got to meet @mckennagraceful tonight at her FIRST ever concert!! It was incredible!! Congrats McKenna! Can’t wait to see you again some day! #mckennagrace #mckennagraceconcert #losangeles #moroccanlounge @moroccanlounge
Poor Charlie 🫣🤣the next day we went tubing and she had a lot more fun.
I forgot to share Bella’s version of the ceilings tend. You have to wait for the end. I love it so much 😂

This girl had a rough day! A bench fell on her foot and broke her big toe and ripped the toenail out from the base. It was so awful! She’s a tough girl though! She’s home with her foot up and it’s gonna take a good long time to heal but we are glad it wasn’t worse! Message me if you want the gory pic! I don’t want to post it because it’s pretty graphic 😖🤢
Super old photo but I never posted this hairstyle. I have a broken arm and of course all I want to do is braid right now when I haven’t even done it in ages 🤣
Ready to watch a live taping of @agt we are so excited!!! #agt #agt #oncameraaudiences @oncameraaudiences
Can’t wait for it to start! @agt @jayflats #agtfinale
Bella has been taking voice lessons and Charlie is learning to play the ukulele. I’m loving it 🥰 so proud of my girls
